                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860531-37-off208 t17860531-37-cd209"></join>, one cotton counterpane, value 2 s. two pillowcases, value 12 d. two flat irons, value 12 d.<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178605310063"></xptr> a tub, value 4 d. two knives, value 4 d. and two forks, value 4 d. the property of 
                     
